data.title: Denver Nuggets Roster
data.meta_description: Denver Nuggets scores, news, schedule, players, stats, rumors, depth charts and more on RealGM.com
data.text:
Vlatko Cancar was selected as the #19 pick in the Second Round of the 2017 NBA Draft by the Denver Nuggets. Vlatko Cancar signed a multi-year contract with the Denver Nuggets on August 1, 2019.

Nikola Jokic was selected as the #11 pick in the Second Round of the 2014 NBA Draft by the Denver Nuggets. Nikola Jokic signed a multi-year contract with the Denver Nuggets on July 12, 2015. Nikola Jokic re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Denver Nuggets on July 9, 2018.

Jamal Murray was selected as the #7 pick in the First Round of the 2016 NBA Draft by the Denver Nuggets. Jamal Murray signed a multi-year contract with the Denver Nuggets on July 19, 2016. Jamal Murray signed a multi-year extension with the Denver Nuggets on July 24, 2019.

Michael Porter, Jr. was selected as the #14 pick in the First Round of the 2018 NBA Draft by the Denver Nuggets. Michael Porter, Jr. signed a multi-year contract with the Denver Nuggets on July 3, 2018.

Will Barton was acquired in a trade by the Denver Nuggets from the Portland Trail Blazers on February 19, 2015. Will Barton re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Denver Nuggets on July 23, 2015. Will Barton re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Denver Nuggets on July 9, 2018.

Keita Bates-Diop was acquired in a trade by the Denver Nuggets from the Minnesota Timberwolves on February 5, 2020.

Jerami Grant was acquired in a trade by the Denver Nuggets from the Oklahoma City Thunder on July 8, 2019.

Mason Plumlee was acquired in a trade by the Denver Nuggets from the Portland Trail Blazers on February 13, 2017. Mason Plumlee re-signed to a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Denver Nuggets on September 20, 2017.

Noah Vonleh was acquired in a trade by the Denver Nuggets from the Minnesota Timberwolves on February 5, 2020.

Torrey Craig signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Denver Nuggets on July 9, 2018.

Troy Daniels signed a contract as a free agent with the Denver Nuggets on March 5, 2020.

P.J. Dozier signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Denver Nuggets on June 30, 2020.

Paul Millsap signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Denver Nuggets on July 13, 2017.

Monte Morris signed a multi-year contract as a free agent with the Denver Nuggets on July 25, 2018.
